 <%- include('../layouts/flash') %>
 <style>
    :root {
      --section-padding: 4rem;
      --heading-size: 2.2rem;
      --subheading-size: 1.4rem;
      --text-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #333;
    }

    .section {
      padding: var(--section-padding) 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: var(--heading-size);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: var(--subheading-size);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p, li {
      font-size: var(--text-size);
    }

    .about-image img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1.5rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .tech-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .tech-list li::before {
      content: "✅ ";
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
      color: green;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- About Me Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center gy-4">
        <h2 class="text-center my-4 p-1" style="background-color: #ffe4c4;">About Me</h2>
        <div class="col-md-6 about-image d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <img src="/images/adiPhoto.jpeg" alt="Pradeep Kumar"  style="height: 20rem;width: 20rem;"/>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <p style="text-align: justify;" class="p-1">Hi! I'm <strong>Pradeep Kumar</strong>, a passionate and detail-oriented web developer currently pursuing my MCA at KCMT College. I specialize in building dynamic, responsive websites and full-stack applications using modern technologies.</p>
          <p>I thrive on continuous learning and love translating ideas into working digital solutions. Whether it's a portfolio, booking system, blog, or admin dashboard — I enjoy solving problems through clean and efficient code.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
   <hr/>
  <!-- Technologies Section -->
  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4 p-1"style="background-color: #ffe4c4;">Skills & Technologies</h2>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p class="p-1">I am consistently enhancing my skills in both front-end and back-end development. Here's a snapshot of my current tech stack:</p>
          <ul class="tech-list p-1">
            <li>HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap 5</li>
            <li>JavaScript (ES6+), DOM Manipulation</li>
            <li>Node.js & Express.js</li>
            <li>MongoDB with Mongoose</li>
            <li>EJS Templating Engine</li>
            <li>REST API Development</li>
            <li>Authentication using Passport.js & Bcrypt</li>
            <li>Version Control with Git & GitHub</li>
            <li>Deployment using Render & Vercel</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
   <hr/>
  <!-- Internship Experience Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4 p-1"style="background-color: #ffe4c4;">Internship Experience</h2>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <p class="text-align justify p-1" >I recently completed a Web Development Internship where I worked on real-world tasks and collaborative projects. During this internship, I:</p>
          <ul class="tech-list p-1">
            <li>Developed a RESTful API for a book management system</li>
            <li>Created and deployed a blog section with admin control</li>
            <li>Implemented secure login systems using sessions and hashed passwords</li>
            <li>Built features such as contact forms, dashboards, and search filters</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="p-1">This hands-on experience helped me refine my project workflow, understand best practices, and prepare for real development challenges.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <hr/>
  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="section bg-light text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center p-1" style="background-color: #ffe4c4;">Let’s Connect!</h2>
      <p class="p-1">I'm open to internships, freelance work, and collaborative projects. If you’re looking for a committed and curious developer — let’s talk!</p>
      <a href="/pradeepkumar/contact" class="btn btn-outline-warning mt-3">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </section>
   <hr/>
</body>
